    "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223460/extras/61db292aa041598558e5414563032b2c.avif?t=1742927173\" width=648 height=246 /></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223460/extras/36d6ab7103d50e72c880d3b4b0f8502b.avif?t=1742927173\" width=367 height=79 /></span><br><br>Guardians and Gods fight for earth's balance<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223460/extras/2cd0e5b6270bafcaf6792171b5fee3d9.avif?t=1742927173\" width=367 height=79 /></span><br><br><br>The earth for thousands of years has been controlled by four <br>gods in charge of the seasons and four guardians who guard <br>the delicate balance of the earth.<br>Humans with their pollution are about to end the balance of <br>the earth, global warming is the trigger for the great <br>sacred war to begin.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223460/extras/15639384a14e369e7512209a96cfb64c.avif?t=1742927173\" width=367 height=79 /></span><br><br>Currently, the game includes:<br><br>- 8 playable characters<br>- 8 stages<br>- Story mode for all 8 characters <br>- Dialogues between fights<br>- killer insting style combo system<br>- 8 original music themes<br>- Vs. AI mode<br>- Training mode <br>- Arcade Stick arcade support<br>- A controller is required for local multiplayer.",
